… Valerius Bassus optio of the legio I Minervia Pia Fidelis has fulfilled a vow willingly and deservedly for himself and for his family.</p></div><div type="apparatus" part="N" org="uniform" sample="complete"><app loc="#MIN.3 #MAJ.3"><note anchored="true">Valer – AE 1893</note></app><app loc="#MIN.4 #MAJ.4"><note anchored="true">ohne Ligatur – Friedrich</note></app><app loc="#MIN.5 #MAJ.5"><note anchored="true">M(inerviae) p(iae) f(idelis) – AE 1893, Lehner, Friedrich</note></app><app loc="#MIN.6 #MAJ.6"><note anchored="true">[pro s]e êt – Lehner; [pro s]e et – Friedrich</note></app></div><div type="commentary" subtype="general" part="N" org="uniform" sample="complete"><p part="N">Valerius Bassus: römisches Namensformular ohne Praenomen <lb/>
